    "description": {
      "content": "The W3C API provides programmatic access to W3C data including specifications,\nworking groups, editors, translations, and affiliations.\n\nAll access is over HTTPS via `api.w3.org`. Data is returned as JSON with\nISO 8601 timestamps. No authentication is required; the rate limit is\n6000 requests per IP per 10 minutes.\n\nDocumentation: https://api.w3.org/doc\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: W3C",
